After an hour or so; Celeron had dug out the pod.  He laid it out on level ground and began to decypher the control panel.

&quot;What kind of pod is this?&quot;

After much trouble, Celeron managed to unlock the pod.  He pulled the lid open and saw a pair of eyes looking back at him.  Malicous looking eyes.  He slammed the lid shut an locked it.

He brushed off the side of the pod and found that this was one of the prisioners from the ship.  An especially violent prisioner because a few seconds later he began to try to break out of the pod.

I better call the Warden.  He runs away just as the pod errupts in flames.

